---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
import CallToAction from "../components/CallToAction.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";

const lang = "fr";
---

<Layout
  title="Pachatopia - Là où la Terre se régénère"
  description="Projet de régénération écologique et humaine à San Carlos en Colombie : forêts, sols, agroforesterie, café, accueil et volontariat."
  lang={lang}
>
  <Header lang={lang} />
  <main>
    <Hero lang={lang} />

    <!-- Une terre qui renaît -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg class="absolute -top-6 right-0 w-64 h-64 opacity-[0.06]" viewBox="0 0 200 200" fill="none">
          <path d="M140 20C140 20 180 60 170 110C160 160 120 180 80 170C40 160 20 120 30 80C40 40 80 20 140 20Z" fill="#0A5B4B"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-8">Une terre qui renaît</h2>
            <div class="space-y-5 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              <p>San Carlos est une région d'une grande beauté naturelle, mais qui a été profondément marquée par l'histoire du conflit armé colombien.</p>
              <p>Aujourd'hui, la nature et les communautés se reconstruisent.</p>
              <p>À Pachatopia, nous croyons que prendre soin de la Terre peut aussi contribuer à reconstruire les liens entre les êtres humains.</p>
              <p>En plantant des arbres, en régénérant les sols et en cultivant la biodiversité, nous participons humblement à cette renaissance.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="relative w-full max-w-md overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
              <img src="/images/farm-hero.jpg" alt="Paysage de San Carlos" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/20 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Nos actions -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-cream">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-14">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">Nos actions</h2>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="block w-8 h-[2px] bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M17 8C8 10 5.9 16.17 3.82 21.34L5.71 22l1-2.3A4.49 4.49 0 008 20c4 0 4-4 8-4s4 4 8 4a4.49 4.49 0 001.29-.34L17 8z"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="block w-8 h-[2px] bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">À Pachatopia, nous développons plusieurs initiatives complémentaires pour restaurer les écosystèmes et soutenir les communautés locales.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8m0 0c-2.5-3-5-5-5-8a5 5 0 0110 0c0 3-2.5 5-5 8z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 21h10"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-3">Régénération des forêts</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Création de réserves naturelles et programmes de reforestation pour protéger la biodiversité et les sources d'eau.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8m0 0c-2.5-3-5-5-5-8a5 5 0 0110 0c0 3-2.5 5-5 8z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-3">Agriculture agroforestière</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Développement de systèmes agricoles inspirés de la nature pour produire des aliments tout en régénérant les sols.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-earth/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-earth" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8C17 8 15 4 12 4C9 4 7 8 7 12C7 16 9 20 12 20C15 20 17 16 17 12"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4C12 4 10 8 10 12C10 16 12 20 12 20"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 12C19 12 21 10 21 8C21 6 19 4 17 4"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-3">Café Pachatopia</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Un café cultivé dans un écosystème vivant, en transition vers l'agroforesterie régénérative.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-golden/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-golden-dark" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-3">Accueil et partage</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Un lieu d'échange et de rencontre où visiteurs et volontaires peuvent découvrir la nature et participer au projet.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center mt-12">
          <a href="/nos-actions/" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-golden text-primary font-semibold text-lg px-10 py-4 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-golden-dark hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-golden/25 hover:-translate-y-0.5">
            <span>Découvrir nos actions</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Un projet vivant -->
    <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary via-primary to-accent/90 overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Organic background shapes -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg class="absolute -top-10 -right-20 w-[500px] h-[500px] opacity-[0.07]" viewBox="0 0 500 500" fill="none">
          <circle cx="250" cy="250" r="240" fill="white"/>
        </svg>
        <svg class="absolute -bottom-16 -left-16 w-[350px] h-[350px] opacity-[0.05]" viewBox="0 0 400 400" fill="none">
          <path d="M200 10C200 10 380 80 370 220C360 360 240 390 160 370C80 350 10 240 30 140C50 40 200 10 200 10Z" fill="white"/>
        </svg>
        <svg class="absolute top-20 left-[8%] w-14 h-14 opacity-[0.12] text-cream" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M50 5C50 5 90 30 90 65C90 82 72 95 50 95C28 95 10 82 10 65C10 30 50 5 50 5Z"/>
        </svg>
        <svg class="absolute bottom-16 right-[12%] w-10 h-10 opacity-[0.10] text-golden" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M50 5C50 5 90 30 90 65C90 82 72 95 50 95C28 95 10 82 10 65C10 30 50 5 50 5Z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm mb-8">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-golden" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8m0 0c-2.5-3-5-5-5-8a5 5 0 0110 0c0 3-2.5 5-5 8z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-10">Un projet vivant</h2>

        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-5">
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed">Pachatopia est un projet en évolution.</p>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/85 leading-relaxed">Chaque année, nous plantons des arbres, restaurons de nouvelles parcelles et développons des initiatives pour renforcer la biodiversité et la résilience du territoire.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 my-10">
          <span class="block w-12 h-[1px] bg-golden/40"></span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-golden/70" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M17 8C8 10 5.9 16.17 3.82 21.34L5.71 22l1-2.3A4.49 4.49 0 008 20c4 0 4-4 8-4s4 4 8 4a4.49 4.49 0 001.29-.34L17 8z"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="block w-12 h-[1px] bg-golden/40"></span>
        </div>

        <blockquote>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-golden font-heading font-semibold italic leading-relaxed">
            «&nbsp;Petit à petit, une forêt et un écosystème régénératif prennent forme.&nbsp;»
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- L'écosystème Pachatopia -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-cream">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">L'écosystème Pachatopia</h2>
          <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-golden rounded-full mx-auto mb-6"></div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Pachatopia est conçu comme un lieu où différentes activités se soutiennent mutuellement.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8m0 0c-2.5-3-5-5-5-8a5 5 0 0110 0c0 3-2.5 5-5 8z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 21h10"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary text-sm">Réserve naturelle</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-earth/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-earth" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8C17 8 15 4 12 4C9 4 7 8 7 12C7 16 9 20 12 20C15 20 17 16 17 12"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary text-sm">Café et cacao</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8m0 0c-2.5-3-5-5-5-8a5 5 0 0110 0c0 3-2.5 5-5 8z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary text-sm">Pépinière d'arbres</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-golden/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-golden-dark" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 21v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h5.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21m0 0h4.5V3.545M12.75 21h7.5V10.75M2.25 21h1.5m18 0h-18M2.25 9l4.5-1.636M18.75 3l-1.5.545m0 6.205l3 1m1.5.5l-1.5-.5M6.75 7.364V3h-3v18m3-13.636l10.5-3.819"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary text-sm">Espace d'accueil</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 col-span-2 sm:col-span-1">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8.25v-1.5m0 1.5c-1.355 0-2.697.056-4.024.166C6.845 8.51 6 9.473 6 10.608v2.513m6-4.87c1.355 0 2.697.055 4.024.165C17.155 8.51 18 9.473 18 10.608v2.513m-3-4.87v-1.5m-6 1.5v-1.5m12 9.75l-1.5.75a3.354 3.354 0 01-3 0 3.354 3.354 0 00-3 0 3.354 3.354 0 01-3 0 3.354 3.354 0 00-3 0 3.354 3.354 0 01-3 0L3 16.5m15-3.38a48.474 48.474 0 00-6-.37c-2.032 0-4.034.126-6 .37m12 0c.39.049.777.102 1.163.16 1.07.16 1.837 1.094 1.837 2.175v5.17c0 .62-.504 1.124-1.125 1.124H4.125A1.125 1.125 0 013 20.625v-5.17c0-1.08.768-2.014 1.837-2.174A47.78 47.78 0 016 13.12M12.265 3.11a.375.375 0 11-.53 0L12 2.845l.265.265z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary text-sm">Cuisine locale</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-center text-lg text-gray-600 mt-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Un projet qui cherche à démontrer qu'il est possible de produire, protéger et partager en harmonie avec la nature.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Participer à l'aventure -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">Participer à l'aventure</h2>
          <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-golden rounded-full mx-auto mb-6"></div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">Pachatopia est une aventure collective.<br/>Chacun peut contribuer à cette dynamique de régénération.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-10">
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8m0 0c-2.5-3-5-5-5-8a5 5 0 0110 0c0 3-2.5 5-5 8z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Planter des arbres</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-earth/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-earth" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8C17 8 15 4 12 4C9 4 7 8 7 12C7 16 9 20 12 20C15 20 17 16 17 12"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Découvrir le café</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S17.66 5 16 5c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3s1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5C6.34 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Participer comme volontaire</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-golden/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-golden-dark" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Soutenir le développement</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-lg text-primary font-medium italic mb-8">Chaque geste compte.</p>
          <a href="/comment-participer/" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-golden text-primary font-semibold text-lg px-10 py-4 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-golden-dark hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-golden/25 hover:-translate-y-0.5">
            <span>Participer au projet</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Notre conviction -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-cream">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-10 md:p-14 border-l-4 border-golden">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-8">Notre conviction</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">Nous croyons que :</p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <p class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-gray-700">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8m0 0c-2.5-3-5-5-5-8a5 5 0 0110 0c0 3-2.5 5-5 8z"/></svg>
              </span>
              Régénérer la Terre peut aider à régénérer les relations humaines
            </p>
            <p class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-gray-700">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8m0 0c-2.5-3-5-5-5-8a5 5 0 0110 0c0 3-2.5 5-5 8z"/></svg>
              </span>
              Planter des arbres est un acte d'espoir
            </p>
            <p class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-gray-700">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-golden/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-golden-dark" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747"/></svg>
              </span>
              Chaque action positive peut inspirer un changement plus vaste
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <CallToAction lang={lang} />
  </main>
  <Footer lang={lang} />
</Layout>
